acklog, InetAddress ifAddress) throws IOException {\\n            if (used) {\\n                throw new IllegalStateException(\\\"Server socket already created\\\");\\n            }\\n            used = true;\\n            return serverSocket;\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 804, \"output\": 833, \"cacheRead\": 10752, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 12389, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\", \"timestamp\": 1777516004875, \"responseId\": \"resp_087221b73c66aa3d0169f2bde53604819dbf447687e38803f8\"}, \"toolResults\": [{\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_VT2UfVrTXTToGDPMZhfHwPo7|fc_087221b73c66aa3d0169f2bde7ec10819d9ae42d8ef97e12b0\", \"toolName\": \"write\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Successfully wrote 3466 bytes to tests/src/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.2.10/src/test/java/ch_qos_logback/logback_core/RemoteReceiverStreamClientTest.java\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777516010499}]}\n678:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_OLlp7cocD32n4CkvnHtCiqbS|fc_087221b73c66aa3d0169f2bdedaffc819d90a565ef27ab35cf\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"?? metadata/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.2.10/\\n?? tests/src/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.2.10/src/test/java/ch_qos_logback/logback_core/RemoteReceiverStreamClientTest.java\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777516014096}}\n679:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_OLlp7cocD32n4CkvnHtCiqbS|fc_087221b73c66aa3d0169f2bdedaffc819d90a565ef27ab35cf\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"?? metadata/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.2.10/\\n?? tests/src/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.2.10/src/test/java/ch_qos_